der tate mayner.

00:27:40.731 --> 00:27:43.745
hobn, hot gevoynt a shokhn

00:27:44.022 --> 00:27:45.366
a RABBI

00:27:46.468 --> 00:27:50.579
iz er flegt araynkumen zikh fregn vos der tate makht

00:27:52.257 --> 00:27:55.980
ts- ruft er mikh avek un zogt tsu mir azoy.

00:27:56.239 --> 00:27:57.667
"Leyele

00:27:58.163 --> 00:28:01.076
der tate halt bay opshtarbn.

00:28:01.504 --> 00:28:04.822
ikh vil az du zolst nemen khupe kidushn

00:28:05.284 --> 00:28:07.190
far der tate shtarbt."

00:28:07.190 --> 00:28:08.510
un azoy iz geven.

00:28:08.510 --> 00:28:10.813
un dos iz geven mayn khasene.

00:28:11.427 --> 00:28:13.615
kh'hob nisht gehat keyn khasene.

00:28:14.818 --> 00:28:18.474
kh'hob genumen khupe kidushn barn tatn's bet.

00:28:19.392 --> 00:28:21.242
dos iz geven mayn lebn.

00:28:25.264 --> 00:28:27.772
kh'hob a sakh mitgemakht in lebn.

00:28:28.318 --> 00:28:29.864
zeyer a sakh.

00:28:32.807 --> 00:28:34.066
un ikh gedenk

00:28:34.123 --> 00:28:36.699
ven m'iz gegebn in Rusland

00:28:36.756 --> 00:28:39.517
vi s'hot gekontshet zikh di milkhome

00:28:40.283 --> 00:28:41.571
in Rusland

00:28:41.571 --> 00:28:44.108
velekhes yor iz dos gevezn?

00:28:44.822 --> 00:28:46.318
ikh gedenk shoyn nisht.

00:28:48.957 --> 00:28:52.379
hob ikh gezogt ikh vil forn aheym.

00:28:52.379 --> 00:28:54.671
ikh vil nisht zayn in Rusland.

00:28:56.753 --> 00:28:58.181
hot men mir

00:28:58.963 --> 00:29:00.825
aroyfgesh-

00:29:00.825 --> 00:29:03.530
-shtelt oyf, oyf di shif

00:29:04.515 --> 00:29:06.264
in Rusland

00:29:07.266 --> 00:29:10.601
hot men mikh aroyfgeshtelt oyf di shif

00:29:10.928 --> 00:29:13.200
un m'hot mir epes gegebn epes

00:29:13.273 --> 00:29:16.594
a por zl- a por zlotes tsi

00:29:16.594 --> 00:29:17.975
a por rubl

00:29:19.213 --> 00:29:21.536
un m'iz geforn keyn Poyln.

00:29:22.048 --> 00:29:28.302
kh'hob a sakh mitgemakht in lebn. dos, der kop ken nisht azoy fil far- gedenken ales.

00:29:28.596 --> 00:29:31.190
me kumt tsu di ende fun di ershte TAPE.

00:29:31.077 --> 00:29:31.833
he?

00:29:31.896 --> 00:29:34.956
me kumt tsu di ende fun di ershte TAPE.
